*Wharf Mail	normal/MailBox2 ExecInTerm "Pine" if(xterm){-fa Monospace -fs 12} -title "Pine e-mail and news reader" -e pine &
*Wharf Mail	normal/MailBox2 Exec "Wharf extras" afterstepdoc extras.html &


