*Wharf IRC  normal/IRCTransparent Exec "HexChat" hexchat &
*Wharf IRC  normal/IRCTransparent ExecInTerm "WeeChat" if(xterm){-fa Monospace -fs 12 -fg white -bg black} -e weechat &
*Wharf IRC  normal/IRCTransparent ExecInTerm "irssi" if(xterm){-fa Monospace -fs 12 -fg white -bg black} -e irssi &
*Wharf IRC	normal/IRCTransparent ExecInTerm "BitchX" -title "BitchX IRC" if(urxvt){-tr -fg white -bg black} if(aterm){-tr -sh 50 -fg white -bg black} if(Eterm){-O --shade 50 -f white -b black) if(rxvt){-tr -fg white -bg black} if(xterm){-fa Monospace -fs 12 -fg white -bg black} -e BitchX irc.libera.chat &
*Wharf IRC  normal/IRCTransparent Exec "Wharf extras" afterstepdoc extras.html &


# subfolder full of games :
*Wharf Games - Category "Games"
*Wharf Games normal/GameController Exec "Wharf extras" afterstepdoc extras.html &


#
# First available Audio player :
#
*Wharf AudioPlayer normal/MusicalNote Exec "mpv" mpv &
*Wharf AudioPlayer normal/MusicalNote Exec "VLC" vlc &
*Wharf AudioPlayer normal/MusicalNote Exec "Audacious" audacious &
*Wharf AudioPlayer normal/MusicalNote Exec "Rhythmbox" rhythmbox &
*Wharf AudioPlayer normal/MusicalNote Exec "Spotify" spotify &
*Wharf AudioPlayer logos/Xmms Exec "X Multi Media System" xmms &
*Wharf AudioPlayer - Swallow "wmxmms2" wmxmms2 -c blue &
*Wharf AudioPlayer - Swallow "wmxmms" wmxmms --single &
*Wharf AudioPlayer - Swallow "ascd" ascd &
*MonitorWharf AudioPlayer - Swallow "wmusic" wmusic -w &
*MonitorWharf AudioPlayer normal/MusicalNote Exec "Music player" sh -lc 'for p in rhythmbox vlc mpv audacious spotify; do command -v "$p" >/dev/null 2>&1 && exec "$p"; done; afterstepdoc extras.html' &
*Wharf AudioPlayer normal/MusicalNote Exec "Wharf extras" afterstepdoc extras.html &

#
# Mixer
#
*Wharf mixer normal/Speaker Exec "PulseAudio Volume Control" pavucontrol &
*Wharf mixer - Swallow "AlsaMixer.app" AlsaMixer.app -1 Master -2 Master -3 Master &
*Wharf mixer - Swallow "wmmixer" wmmixer &
*Wharf mixer - Swallow "asmixer" asmixer -g -1-1 &
*Wharf mixer - Swallow "asMix" asmix -shape &
*Wharf mixer normal/Speaker ExecInTerm "-" if(xterm){-fa Monospace -fs 12 -T Mixer} -e sh -lc 'command -v alsamixer >/dev/null 2>&1 && exec alsamixer; command -v pulsemixer >/dev/null 2>&1 && exec pulsemixer; afterstepdoc extras.html' &
*Wharf mixer normal/Speaker Exec "Wharf extras" afterstepdoc extras.html &

